{"tid":1179213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓足球員向獎杯小便後全隊道歉　中國當局決收回獎盃","createTime":"2019-05-31T03:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T04:47:10.000Z","uid":117200,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1b630e9703c1d8e4ec95d736393a18a7ed7850","tid":1179213,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2147-6/p540x282/61875507_1154107214772270_8391740547282239488_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=8345abbea4572ce946304f40f40b6670&amp;oe=5D5D8F44\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2147-6%2Fp540x282%2F61875507_1154107214772270_8391740547282239488_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D8345abbea4572ce946304f40f40b6670%26oe%3D5D5D8F44&h=606b01e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓足球隊日前到中國參加「熊貓杯」國際青年足球錦標賽，未料獲得冠軍後竟腳踩獎盃拍照，甚至對獎盃做出小便等不雅舉動，不滿的中國主辦方向南韓足協抗議。<br />\n<br />\n最終該南韓球隊全員在30日凌晨於下榻飯店集體公開鞠躬道歉。球隊的主將表示：「我們希望兩國足協能維持友好關係，我們的球員不會再做出類似舉動，我們再次道歉，我們傷害了中國人的感情。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/j.PCJWQT2aPXwGpOgHEuUA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/en-us/upmedia.mg.tw/e1a50fe70a270c7aef5cae352ef53954\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fj.PCJWQT2aPXwGpOgHEuUA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen-us%2Fupmedia.mg.tw%2Fe1a50fe70a270c7aef5cae352ef53954&h=15fe7734&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SamjNxcLd2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSamjNxcLd2w&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=8ae2903e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SamjNxcLd2w</a><br />\n<br />\n網民:<br />\n<br />\nyc cy:韓國就是鄉巴佬，不要命也一樣不要臉。不喜歡但是不得不多加小心。居然有韓粉也是中國今天的悲哀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJian Dong:韓國人素質差的就像他那張臉，一看就是天生的賤貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJesus Christ:你他媽踢球真像中國男人"},{"pid":"9b71cda97ca0ff08204ee2c821212aa4d5d31403","tid":1179213,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:20:26.000Z","msg":"內地或成最大贏家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0ada560dacfa4df0ddb30f2016c9ef6107440f","tid":1179213,"uid":232849,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:22:15.000Z","msg":"南韓球員: 我地唔想拎哩舊垃圾返去喎。<br />\n教練: 我有計，聽我指示。"},{"pid":"b7bfe88e15e1bf7e5d8b8e6a4f20eebb96242bc7","tid":1179213,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d6cfbd0a27e75e97e8fd399c8a13a2d507188e","tid":1179213,"uid":60109,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:51:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得中國女排應該公開對住南韓女排痾尿囉"},{"pid":"2ae501a5d15c04b6e99ac3d91d508268b5ac4946","tid":1179213,"uid":38194,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:52:48.000Z","msg":"兩邊都唔係好人"},{"pid":"21b9c812f872f5c9f74e434e908a05bb6bee9bfe","tid":1179213,"uid":12021,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:53:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be4c4ea45906f7869ddd6633af66f4b107d836ad","tid":1179213,"uid":53855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:54:31.000Z","msg":"有冇扮撒尿嘅睇相睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1e38e93782faeda212cbd641576f4b0e0ba963","tid":1179213,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08d6cfbd0a27e75e97e8fd399c8a13a2d507188e","tid":1179213,"uid":60109,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:51:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得中國女排應該公開對住南韓女排痾尿囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:5